<pre><a name="Haiku"><STRONG>Haiku</STRONG></a><STRONG>
      by Daniel Kuznicki
      Daniel is a fifth grader at Readington Middle School.</STRONG></pre>
<pre><STRONG><img src="/esoup/gif/trees.jpg" align=middle width=253 height=101>                                                         </STRONG></pre>
<pre><STRONG>                Trees that color the earth
		animals call their home
		     Oh, to be a tree
</STRONG></pre>
<pre><STRONG>The Young Writers section is not exclusively for young writers. 
Boys and Girls, Men and Women, Young and Old, can
contribute, too, if you deem your work proper for young
children to read.  Always, always, we are interested in the
work of young writers!</STRONG></pre>
