<p><STRONG><img src="/esoup/gif/whball.gif" align=bottom width=18 height=18></STRONG><a href="#Mood Swings of a River"><STRONG>Mood Swings of a River</STRONG></a><STRONG> by Ryan Gernay </STRONG></p>
