<body background="/esoup/gif/a075.jpg" text="#FFFF00" link="#00FF00" vlink="#FFFFFF">
<h1 align=center><a name="Top"><STRONG>Electric Soup Poetry</STRONG></a></h1>
<p><STRONG>I cannot imagine how other people live without poetry<br>
because for me, poetry is a way of living my life, <br>
a way of feeling life.<br>
Poet, Daisy Zamora <br>
</STRONG></p>
<p><STRONG>--A poetry editor on break</STRONG></p>
<p><STRONG><img src="/esoup/gif/freder.jpg" align=left width=216 height=181>Pieces in this Volume Include:</STRONG></p>
<p><STRONG><img src="/esoup/gif/purbull.gif" align=bottom width=18 height=18></STRONG><a href="#Divine Intervention"><STRONG>Divine Intervention</STRONG></a><STRONG> by Matt Kuznicki</STRONG></p>
<p><STRONG><img src="/esoup/gif/purbull.gif" align=bottom width=18 height=18></STRONG><a href="#Sunset"><STRONG>Sunset</STRONG></a><STRONG> by Brooke Hennessey</STRONG></p>
<p><STRONG><img src="/esoup/gif/purbull.gif" align=bottom width=18 height=18></STRONG><a href="#Memories of You"><STRONG>My Memories of You, Sir</STRONG></a><STRONG> by Irene Pirgiotis Borkin</STRONG></p>
<p><STRONG><img src="/esoup/gif/purbull.gif" align=bottom width=18 height=18></STRONG><a href="#Whatever Happens"><STRONG>Whatever Happens, Happens</STRONG></a><STRONG> by Jennifer Witt</STRONG></p>
<p><STRONG><img src="/esoup/gif/purbull.gif" align=bottom width=18 height=18></STRONG><a href="#Escape"><STRONG>Escape</STRONG></a><STRONG> by Nicole Baker</STRONG></p>
<p><STRONG><img src="/esoup/gif/purbull.gif" align=bottom width=18 height=18></STRONG><a href="#My Violin"><STRONG>My Violin</STRONG></a><STRONG> by Christina Albrecht</STRONG></p>
<p><STRONG><img src="/esoup/gif/purbull.gif" align=bottom width=18 height=18></STRONG><a href="#Night Falls"><STRONG>Night falls</STRONG></a><STRONG> by Dana Bivona</STRONG></p>
<p><STRONG><img src="/esoup/gif/purbull.gif" align=bottom width=18 height=18></STRONG><a href="#Forgery"><STRONG>Forgery</STRONG></a><STRONG> by Anne McNamara</STRONG></p>
<p><STRONG><img src="/esoup/gif/purbull.gif" align=bottom width=18 height=18></STRONG><a href="#Changes"><STRONG>Changes</STRONG></a><STRONG> by Debbie Chun</STRONG></p>
<p><STRONG><img src="/esoup/gif/purbull.gif" align=bottom width=18 height=18></STRONG><a href="#Corner"><STRONG>Corner</STRONG></a><STRONG> by Carolyn Chun</STRONG></p>
<p><STRONG><img src="/esoup/gif/purbull.gif" align=bottom width=18 height=18></STRONG><a href="#struggle"><STRONG>struggle</STRONG></a><STRONG> by Kristina Sutphen</STRONG></p>
