<p><STRONG><img src="/esoup/gif/purbull.gif" align=bottom width=18 height=18></STRONG><a href="#Wish I could"><STRONG>I wish I could</STRONG></a><STRONG> by Carl Weeks</STRONG></p>
<p><STRONG><img src="/esoup/gif/purbull.gif" align=bottom width=18 height=18></STRONG><a href="#The Blizzard"><STRONG>The Blizzard</STRONG></a><STRONG> by Jerry George</STRONG></p>
