<p><STRONG>Poetry is like bread -- everybody shares it. </STRONG></p>
<p><STRONG>Poet, Claribel Alegria</STRONG></p>
<p><img src="/esoup/gif/green01.jpg" align=right width=242 height=203></p>
<p><STRONG>Pieces in this volume include: </STRONG></p>
<p><STRONG><img src="/esoup/gif/redbull.gif" align=bottom width=18 height=18></STRONG><a href="#harvest"><STRONG>Harvest</STRONG></a><STRONG> by Dan VanAntwerp </STRONG></p>
<p><STRONG><img src="/esoup/gif/redbull.gif" align=bottom width=18 height=18></STRONG><a href="#suitcase"><STRONG>The Suitcase</STRONG></a><STRONG> by Jeannie Gobillot </STRONG></p>
