<pre><STRONG>           You send me your poems, 
		I'll send you mine.</STRONG></pre>
<pre><STRONG>           Things tend to awaken 
		even through random communication.</STRONG></pre>
<pre><STRONG>               from Robert Creeley's &quot;The Conspiracy&quot; 
		    in his collection, </STRONG><STRONG><U>For Love: Poems 1950-1960</U></STRONG><STRONG>


				--Chris McNutt, a Young Writer's Editor</STRONG></pre>
