<html>

<head>
<title>Welcome to Electric Soup</title>
</head>
<body background="gif/a034.jpg" text="#008000" link="#FFFFFF" vlink="#FF0000">
<h1 align=center>Welcome to Electric Soup</h1>

<p><STRONG>Welcome to </STRONG><EM><STRONG>Electric Soup</STRONG></EM><STRONG>, Hunterdon Central's Online Literary Magazine. The name of the 
magazine comes from a student poem by Frederique de Lame: &quot;Quickly seeping into open 
minds/twisting neurons/electric soup blurring into a novel image.&quot;</STRONG></p>
<p><STRONG>Many of the pieces found within the magazine are written by Hunterdon Central Students, 
Staff, and Alumnae as well as pieces written by the &quot;Young&quot; Writers from the sending 
districts of Hunterdon Central. However, </STRONG><EM><STRONG>Electric Soup's</STRONG></EM><STRONG> goal is to be an inclusive, 
responsive literary magazine. We seek work from ALL writers, and contributors need not be 
associated with Hunterdon Central. We invite all submissions supportive of the inquisitive, 
imaginative writing process. But now, please come in!</STRONG></p>
<p><img src="gif/road.jpg" align=right></p>
<p><img src="gif/sound.gif" align=bottom><a href="WELCOME.TSP"><STRONG>Play Greeting</STRONG></a></p>
<p><img src="gif/butterfl.gif" align=bottom><a href="esvol1/esv1toc.html"><STRONG>Read Volume 1</STRONG></a></p>
<p><img src="gif/butterfl.gif" align=bottom><a href="esvol2/esv2toc.html"><STRONG>Read Volume 2</STRONG></a></p>
<p><img src="gif/butterfl.gif" align=bottom><a href="esvol3/esv3toc.html"><STRONG>Read Volume 3</STRONG></a></p>
<p><img src="gif/butterfl.gif" align=bottom><a href="esvol4/esv4toc.html"><strong>Read Volume 4</strong></a></p>
