<H1 ALIGN=CENTER><A NAME="Electric Soup Community"></A><B>Electric Soup
Philosphical Essays</B></H1>

<P><B>Volume 6 contains the following selections:</B></P>

<TABLE>
<TR>
<TD width=30%><IMG SRC="statue2.jpg" HEIGHT=169 WIDTH=114> </TD>

<TD width=70%>
<UL>
<P><A HREF="#Dreams Exist to be Conquered"><IMG SRC="purbull.gif" HEIGHT=18 WIDTH=18></A><B><A HREF="#Dreams Exist to be Conquered">Dreams
Exist to be Conquered</A> by Jessica Terrizzi</B></P>
</UL>

<UL>
<P><A HREF="#Prison or Penthouse?"><IMG SRC="purbull.gif" HEIGHT=18 WIDTH=18></A><B><A HREF="#Prison or Penthouse?">Prison
or Penthouse?</A> by Ryan Gernay</B></P>

<P><A HREF="#The Prozac Addiction"><IMG SRC="purbull.gif" HEIGHT=18 WIDTH=18></A><B><A HREF="#The Prozac Addiction">The
Prozac Addiction</A> by Lisa Routel</B></P>
</UL>

<P><B>Click here to&nbsp;Return to the <A HREF="esv6toc.html">Volume 6
Main Menu</A></B></P>
</TD>
</TR>
