<H1 ALIGN=CENTER><A NAME="Electric Soup Community"></A><B>Electric Soup
Magnetic, Linked </B></H1>

<H1 ALIGN=CENTER><B>and Form Poetry</B></H1>

<P><B>Volume 6 contains the following selections:</B></P>

<TABLE>
<TR>
<TD WIDTH=20%><IMG SRC="psalley.jpg" HEIGHT=178 WIDTH=124></TD>

<TD WIDTH=70%>
<UL>
<P><A HREF="#Retrospect"><IMG SRC="redbull.gif" HEIGHT=18 WIDTH=18></A><B><A HREF="#Retrospect">Retrospect</A>
by Katie Lynch and Dan DeLorenzo</B></P>

<P><A HREF="#WINTER'S CALM TEMPEST"><IMG SRC="redbull.gif" HEIGHT=18 WIDTH=18></A><B><A HREF="#WINTER'S CALM TEMPEST">Winter's
Calm Tempest</A> by Erin Schneiderman and Rob Wavra</B></P>

<P><A HREF="#FOREST WHISPERS"><IMG SRC="redbull.gif" HEIGHT=18 WIDTH=18></A><B><A HREF="#FOREST WHISPERS">Forest
Whispers</A> by Jarrett Basedow</B></P>

