in the white dust</A> by Jarrett Basedow</B></P>
</TD>

<TD WIDTH=50%><A HREF="#HAIKU"><IMG SRC="redbull.gif" HEIGHT=18 WIDTH=18></A><B><A HREF="#HAIKU">darkness
envelopes</A> by Alison Euairoli</B>
