<TD width=5%></TD>

<TD width=65%><A NAME="Lost Prayers -- Edmond's thoughts during"></A><B>Lost
Prayers -- Edmond's thoughts during imprisonment at the Chateau d'lf --
from <U>The Count of Monte Cristo</U> </B>
<P><B>by Hayley Pierce </B></P>

<P><B><I>Hayley wrote this as an eighth-grader at Far Hills County Day
School. Presently, she is a high school freshman.</I> </B></P>
</TD>

<TD width=30%><IMG SRC="2sm.jpg" HEIGHT=161 WIDTH=239></TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>

<TABLE>
<TR>
<TD width=5%></TD>

<TD width=65%><B>Many years I've wasted in this gloomy prison cell </B>
<P><B>I'm sure I'd rather die than live my whole life in this hell. </B></P>

<P><B>I rise at dawn with morning and I count the days gone by </B></P>

<P><B>I pray to God each sunset, but I wait with no reply. </B></P>

<P><B>I feel my eyes and senses grow accustomed to the black </B></P>

<P><B>I know not why I lost my freedom, but I want it back. </B></P>

<P><B>The azure sky and rolling clouds seem all so far away </B></P>

<P><B>When I look out my window -- through my captor -- bars of gray. </B></P>

<P><B>The repetition drives me mad, it all stays quite the same, </B></P>

<P><B>The food, the clothes, my thoughts, my foes; I'm prisoner of this
game. </B></P>

<P><B>I tell you, this could make a man as mad as he could be, </B></P>

<P><B>Shut up inside his dungeon with his thoughts of being free. </B></P>

<P><B>Return to <A HREF="#Electric Soup Community">Young Writers Menu</A></B></P>
</TD>

<TD width=30%></TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>

<P><IMG SRC="barfrac1.gif" HEIGHT=17 WIDTH=555></P>

<TABLE>
<TR>
<TD width=5%></TD>

<TD width=65%><A NAME="Hat Rack"></A><B>Hat Rack </B>
<P><B>by Jonathan Miller </B></P>

<P><BR>
<BR>
</P>

<P><B>It sat, abandoned for twelve years </B></P>

<P><B>At six years of age it entered my life, </B></P>

<P><B>And struck sheer terror in my soul </B></P>

<P><B>For at night, as I crept to my room, </B></P>

<P><B>It would snap and claw at me, </B></P>

<P><B>It was a beast of hats and fur scarves. </B></P>

<P><B>For it to once again be bedtime, </B></P>

<P><B>And for me to once again creep to my room.</B></P>

<P><B>Return to <A HREF="#Electric Soup Community">Young Writers Menu</A></B></P>
</TD>

<TD width=30%></TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>

