of rocks while on the outside bend, the stream is cutting away at the bank.  Gradually,
this stream (one of the many) is wearing away Hunterdon County - gradually wearing 
away the landscape, grinding it down to particle size and transporting those particles
off to the ocean.  (click on picture to continue)
