Centi means 1/100 of something.  For instance, one centimeter equals .01 of a meter, or one-one hundreth of a meter.<br><br>

This is also seen in:<br>
Centigram<br>
Centiliter<br>
Centipede<br>
Century<br>
Cent<br>
Centavo<br>
Centennial<br>
Centigrade<br>
Centillion<br>
