<center><h2><b>Important Conversions</b></h2></center>

1 meter	= 	39.37 inches<br>
1 liter		= 	1.06 quarts<br>
1 kilogram	= 	2.2 pounds<br>
1 mililiter	= 	1 cubic centimeter<br>
1 inch		= 	2.54 centimeters<br>
1 pound	= 	4.54 grams<br>

<b><h4>1 cubic centimeter = 1 mililiter = 1 gram</h4></b>
For example, 537 cubic centimeters = 537 mililiters = 537 grams<br>

