<h1><u><center>Focus and Epicenter</center></u></h1>

<center><u><IMG SRC="gif/smile.gif"><a href="earthgen.html"><h5>Go Back to General Information on Earthquakes</h5></a></u></center><hr>

<UL>
<LI>The<b><u> Focus</u></b> is the actual point of the earthquake.  This is underground.
<LI>The <b><u>Epicenter</u></b> is the point where the earthquake reaches the surface of the earth.</UL>
<a href="fande.html">Go to Top of Focus and Epicenter</a><br>
<a href="earthgen.html">Go Back to General Information on Earthquakes</a>
