<h1><u><center>Earthquake Safety</center></u></h1>

<center><u><IMG SRC="gif/smile.gif"><a href="earthgen.html"><h5>Go Back to General Information on Earthquakes</h5></a></u></center><hr>

<h2><center>If you were home when an earthquake occurred, what would <b>you </b>do?</h2></center><hr>

<h3>What our class would do:
</h3>
<UL>
<LI>Get underneath something large and sturdy
<LI>If possible, get under a doorway
<LI>Protect your head with your arms
<LI>When the shock is over, proceed about carefully.  Objects are not stable and there could be aftershocks.</UL>
