<BR>
</center>

The next stop on our trip is just a few hundred yards along Route 29.  It is in the creekbed known
as Warford Creek.  Here, one can easily observe the erosional effects of water in a tilted streambed.  
(click on picture to continue)
</B>
</HTML>
