</center>

If we hike up one of the many stream beds that empty into the Delaware at this
point, we can observe even more evidence of this massive avalanche.  The entire area
seems to consist of this conglomerate material.  (this formation is knows as the Hammer
Creek Conglomerate.  (click on picture to continue)
</B>
