<HEAD>

<TITLE>Welcome To CHCH On The WWW</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">


<CENTER><IMG HEIGHT=128 WIDTH=529 SRC="../images/welcome.gif" ALT="Welcome To In Touch"></CENTER>

<P>Welcome to CHCH-TV's site on the World Wide Web: <I>In Touch</I>.  

<P>At <I>In Touch</I> we believe in staying in touch with our television viewers and web site visitors.  The <I>In Touch</I> Web Site is constantly evolving and growing, providing useful and entertaining information to our Internet friends.

<P>CHCH-TV covers the Niagara Region with 325,000 watts from an antenna
that sits on the Niagara escarpment 1,744 feet above sea level.
CHCH is owned and operated by <A HREF="../wic/">WIC Western International Communications
Ltd.</A> and licensed by the <A HREF="../crtc/">Canadian Radio-Television and Telecommunications
Commission</A>. CHCH is seen nationwide to cable subscribers in certain
areas via <A HREF="../wic/cancom.htm">Canadian Satellite Communications Inc. (Cancom)</A>.

<P>We hope you will find the <I>In Touch</I> web site entertaining and
informative. If there is some information about CHCH, <I>In Touch</I>, our programs,
or facilities that you would like to see, please leave a note for our <A HREF="mailto:webmaster@chch.wic.ca">Web Editor</A>.
We are always looking for new ideas and user feedback. Thanks
for visiting CHCH-TV <I>In Touch</I>!

<P>
<CENTER>
<A HREF="../mgr/pres.htm">Please also see the message from our President, James B. Macdonald</A>.
<P>
<CENTER><IMG WIDTH=585 HEIGHT=30 SRC="../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="MIDDLE"><BR></CENTER>
