<HEAD>
<TITLE>CHCH Operations & Production</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">
<P>

<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="../images/productn.gif">
</CENTER>

<P>
CHCH offers broadcast quality production and post-production facilities,
as well as professional, highly experienced technical and creative
personnel. 
<P>
Our studios, mobiles, and EFP units are often utilized by third
party producers on projects as varied as sports, drama, music,
and teleconferencing. On-staff writers, producers, and directors
have extensive experience in programming, commercial production,
and corporate video production.
<H4><UL>
<LI><I>Operations</I><BR>
The term &quot;Operations&quot; refers to the technical execution
and/or broadcast of television and video programs, commercials,
info-mercials, and corporate videos. <BR>

<UL>
<LI><A HREF="onair.htm">On-Air </A>Operations
<LI><A HREF="studmobl.htm">Studio &amp; Mobile</A> Facilities   ***See details about our new <A HREF="discovry.htm"><I>Discovery Mobile</I></A>!
<LI>Commercial, Corporate Video &amp; Program Single-Camera/<A HREF="efp.htm">E.F.P.</A>
Facilities
<LI><A HREF="postp.htm">Post-Production</A> Facilities
</UL>
<BR>
<LI><I>Production</I><BR>
The term &quot;Production&quot; refers to the creative writing, budgeting, scheduling, and execution of video material including programs, commercials, corporate videos, and infomercials.
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="prod1.htm">Corporate Video & Commercial Production</A>
</UL>
</UL></H4>

<P>

<CENTER><IMG WIDTH=585 HEIGHT=30 SRC="../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="MIDDLE"><BR></CENTER>
<CENTER>
<TABLE COLSPACE=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 BORDER=0>
<TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="../general/aboutch.htm"><IMG SRC="../images/leftarro.gif" border=0 ALT="Left Arrow Icon"><BR><B>All About CHCH</B></A></TD>
<TD><IMG SRC="../images/blank.gif"></TD>
<TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="/"><IMG SRC="../images/home.gif" border=0 ALT="Home Page Icon"><BR><B>CHCH Home Page</B></A></TD>
<TD><IMG SRC="../images/blank.gif"></TD>
<TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="mailto:webmaster@chch.wic.ca"><IMG SRC="../images/mail.gif" border=0 ALT="Mail Icon"><BR><B>webmaster@chch.wic.ca</B></A></TH></TD>
