<HEAD>

<TITLE>11 In Touch - Answering The Call</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">

<CENTER><IMG WIDTH=210 HEIGHT=148 SRC="../images/ivr.gif" ALIGN="MIDDLE"><BR></CENTER>

<CENTER><H1>Answering the call!</H1></CENTER>
<P>
CHCH TV's new interactive voice response system <I><B>11 In Touch</B></I>
offers you a variety of information choices at the touch of a
button.
<P>
Via 1-888-770-2424 (toll free) or locally (905) 777-2424 callers
from across Ontario can access the <I><B>11 In Touch</B></I> menu
which guides them through a variety of options and instant information
services such as News, Weather, Sports, Business and Entertainment.
 The information is continually updated, is available 24 hours
per day and is changing constantly as new services are added.
<P>
We are enthusiastic about the addition of <I><B>11 In Touch</B></I>.
 It is an extension of our News and Information services to you,
our viewers.  <I><B>11 In Touch</B></I>  also adds another dimension
to the our <A HREF="../general/sales.htm">Integrated Marketing Services</A>
plan by providing CHCH advertisers another vehicle from which
they can present their product or service to potential customers.
<P>
CHCH-TV is also proud of its partnership with Unitel.  As the
Gateway Sponsor of <I><B>11 In Touch</B></I>, Unitel has made
a significant contribution in support of this new service.
<P>
<CENTER><H3>Get In Touch.  Keep in touch.  Call <I><B>11 In Touch</B></I>.</H3></CENTER>

<CENTER><IMG WIDTH=585 HEIGHT=30 SRC="../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="MIDDLE"><BR></CENTER>

<CENTER><H1><I><B>11 In Touch</B></I> Service Menu</H1></CENTER>
<P>
<UL>
<LI>For the latest News, Weather, Sports and Business from the CHCH
<I>News Centre</I>, dial <B>extension 1111</B>.
<P>
<LI>What's happening in the world of entertainment? Dial <B>extension
1112</B> for <I>The Entertainment Report</I> with Alex Reynolds.
<P>
<LI>Community and charitable events can be found on <I>Community File</I>,
<B>extension 1113</B>.
<P>
<LI>Get details about the Smash hit musical Patsy <I><B>and</B></I>
enter the draw to win tickets to the show. Dial <B>extension 2000</B>.
<P>
<LI><I>Coming soon:</I> The Barn Good Food Ideas Line.
</UL>
<P>


<CENTER><IMG WIDTH=585 HEIGHT=30 SRC="../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="MIDDLE"><BR></CENTER>

