<BR><P>Welcome to the Internet and the CHCH-TV <I>In Touch</I> web site.

<P>We are delighted to have this opportunity to speak directly with our
viewers, and get your input regarding our programming and the changes we
are making to CHCH to allow us to compete in the quickly changing
communications landscape.

<P>CHCH-TV <I>In Touch</I> provides you with what we hope will be useful
information about CHCH, our parent company <A HREF="../wic/wic.htm">WIC Western International
Communications Ltd.</A>, and also contains hyperlinks to a number of other
interesting Web sites which we hope you will find a convenient way of
accessing other pages. We hope you will come to regard CHCH-TV <I>In Touch</I> as your launch point to the 'Net'.

<P>We would welcome your suggestions on other 'cool' sites
that we might include in the future.

<P>I look forward to any comments or suggestions you may have on our programs 
or any other way in which we can improve our service to you, which can be done by simply
clicking below.

<P>Send Jim Macdonald an E-Mail message here: <A HREF="mailto:jmac@tor.hookup.net">president@chch.wic.ca</A>
