<HEAD>

<TITLE>Integrated Marketing Services</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">


<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/sales.gif"></CENTER>
<CENTER><H1><I>Integrated Marketing Services</I></H1></CENTER>
<CENTER><H3>A division of CHCH-TV</H3></CENTER>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></CENTER>

<P>
<I><B>The Right Way To Partner</B></I>
<P>
CHCH personnel are experienced advertising and marketing professionals,
with knowledge of and access to, local, national and international
marketing issues. Supported by a highly skilled creative team
and state of the art technology, CHCH can create leading edge
multimedia advertising campaigns that will generate measurable
results for you.
<P>
Our new interactive services will provide timely information that
is routinely updated.
<P>
We can direct connect our caller to your place of business or
link the &quot;surfer&quot; to other interesting web sites around
the world. We can fax back responses, send &quot;bounce back&quot;
direct mail, collect consumer market data, provide fulfillment
services for your product or service and generate new sales leads.
<P>
Your success is our success. to that end CHCH will produce television
promotion campaigns that will feature your partnership with our
interactive services highlighting the telephone number or Internet
address where your advertising message can be found, ensuring
maximum customer response.
