contest testing the knowledge of our visitors. Simply answer the
monthly question and, if your answer is correct, you will be entered
in the random drawing to be held January 2, 1997. All entries
must be received by 9:00am on January 2, 1997. <I>One lucky winner will
receive a CHCH Sweatshirt and the winners' name will be announced
on this page January 2, 1996.</I> 
