<TITLE>WIC Career Opportunities</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">


<CENTER><IMG WIDTH=524 HEIGHT=85 SRC="../images/wic_jo.gif" ALIGN="MIDDLE"><BR></CENTER>

<P>
WIC Western International Communications Ltd. is an integrated Canadian communications, broadcast and entertainment company with its head office in Vancouver, British Columbia.  WIC is the only Canadian broadcasting company operating in television, pay television, radio and satellite network services.
<P>
The following are the current career opportunities within <A HREF="../wic/">WIC Western International Communications</A>:
