<HEAD>

<TITLE>CHCH Programming Schedule</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../../images/bkgd.jpg">
<P>

<CENTER><IMG HEIGHT=87 WIDTH=526 SRC="../../images/prog_pri.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM" ALT="CHCH Primetime Schedule"></CENTER>

<CENTER>
<H1><I>Sunday, December 29 </I> to <I>Saturday, January 4, 1997</I></H1>
</CENTER>

<CENTER>
<I>(cc) denotes the program is closed captioned</I>
</CENTER>

<HR>

<H3><I>Sunday, December 29, 1996</I></H3>

<PRE>
 6:00 PM  <B>Kung Fu: The Legend Continues:</B> &quot;May I Talk With You?&quot; (cc)
 6:30 PM  
