          school in a TV quiz show, nobody expects too much.  But the
          eccentricities that set the four apart as individuals -- their
          unique ways of looking at the world -- somehow make then an
          unbeatable team.</I>
 8:30 PM  
 9:00 PM  The Movies Eleven: <B>&quot;Glory Enough for All - Part 1&quot;</B></A> 
