</PRE>


<P>
<B>Monday, January 6, 1997</B>
<PRE>
 9:00 PM  <B>&quot;The Thriller&quot;</B></A> 
          <I>At an autograph session for her first novel, Sara Levinson meets
          a man who abruptly tells her he is going to be murdered.  After
          she has dinner with him, he is murdered and she realizes that she
          isn't going to write fiction.  Linda Smith and Peter Dvorsky star.</I> 

</PRE>


