<PRE>
 9:00 PM  <B>&quot;The Flood: Who Will Save Our Children&quot;</B> (cc)
          <I>On July 17, 1987, violent rains force the hasty evacuation of a 
          church camp in the Texas hills.  Acts of heroism abound as members
          of the group and rescue workers fight for the lives of others.</I>

</PRE>




