<HEAD>
<TITLE>"Linehan", premieres January 11, 1997 on CHCH-TV.</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY background="../../images/bkgd.jpg">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../../images/release1.gif" ALIGN="MIDDLE"></CENTER>
<H2 ALIGN=RIGHT><I><B>December 23, 1996</B></I></H2> 

<CENTER>
<H1>&quot;Linehan&quot;</H1>
<H2>premieres January 11, 1997 on CHCH-TV.</H2>
</CENTER>

<P>
<I><B>Linehan</B></I>, the new weekly series showcasing the biggest
and brightest names in show business, premieres <U>Saturday, January
11, 1997 (7:00 - 7:30 p.m.)</U>, on <B>CHCH-TV</B>.<BR>

<P>
Hosted by Brian Linehan, one of television's most distinguished
journalists, <I><B>Linehan</B></I> will deliver in-depth interviews
with the stars and the most powerful people in the world of entertainment.
 <BR>

<P>
Featured guests on Linehan's premiere show include <B>Shirley
MacLaine, Martin Short</B> and <B>Marion Ross</B>. <BR>

<P>
Brian Linehan, renowned for his distinctive interviewing style,
returns to television with his half-hour weekly series,<I><B>
Linehan</B></I>, <U>Saturday, January 11, 1997, at 7:00 p.m.</U>
on <B>CHCH-TV</B>.<BR>

<P>
<I><B>Linehan </B></I>is produced by Electric Entertainment for
distribution by WIC television Ltd.<BR>
<BR>
<BR>

<P>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="../../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></CENTER>
<CENTER>
<TABLE COLSPACE=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 BORDER=0>
<TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="../press.htm"><IMG SRC="../../images/leftarro.gif" border=0 ALT="Left Arrow Icon"><BR><B>For Immediate Release</B></A></TD>
<TD><IMG SRC="../../images/blank.gif"></TD>
<TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="/"><IMG SRC="../../images/home.gif" border=0 ALT="Home Page Icon"><BR><B>CHCH Home Page</B></A></TD>
<TD><IMG SRC="../../images/blank.gif"></TD>
<TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="mailto:programming@chch.wic.ca"><IMG SRC="../../images/mail.gif" border=0 ALT="Mail Icon"><BR><B>programming@chch.wic.ca</B></A></TH></TD>
</TABLE></CENTER>
