<HEAD>

<TITLE>CHCH News: The Morning Market</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../../images/bkgd.jpg">
<CENTER>
<IMG HEIGHT=179 WIDTH=345 SRC="../../images/market1.gif">
</CENTER>

<P>
<I><B>The Morning Market</B></I> provides the most complete, up-to-the-minute
financial news and analysis available.  In addition to featuring
financial data, a unique multi-media approach allows hard news,
business travel weather reports and lifestyle information to be
presented simultaneously on screen.  <I><B>The Morning Market</B></I>
utilizes the world-wide resources of Bloomberg, one of the topmost
financial news and information electronic services operating in
real-time globally.

<P>
