<TITLE>CHCH News: News At Noon</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY background="../../images/bkgd.jpg">
<IMG SRC="../../images/noon.gif">

<P>A bright, informative hour of news, entertainment, and valuable lifestyle
information hosted by anchors <A HREF="../biographies/dan.htm">DAN
McLEAN</A> and <A HREF="../biographies/connie.htm">CONNIE SMITH</A>.
 In addition to the days' top stories, roving Reporter <A HREF="../biographies/paul.htm"
>PAUL HENDRICK</A> brings you sports highlights and the weather outlook
for the region. 	The News At Noon is the Golden Horseshoe's
indispensible midday news package.  Weekdays on CHCH-TV.
