<HEAD>
<TITLE>CHCH News: First Edition</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY background="../../images/bkgd.jpg">
<IMG SRC="../../images/first.gif"> 	

<P><A HREF="../biographies/dan.htm">DAN McLEAN</A> and <A HREF="../biographies/connie.htm">CONNIE
SMITH</A>  present the news and issues directly concerning viewers in
the Golden Horseshoe.  The news leader in Southern Ontario, First
Edition originates LIVE from every corner of the community it serves.  
<A HREF="../biographies/paul.htm">PAUL HENDRICK</A> offers
sports from the school gyms and playing fields in the region; and <A HREF="../biographies/matt.htm"
>MATT HAYES</A> presents his unique blend of weather with a light touch
of community happenings. First Edition, weeknights at 5:30pm.<BR>
The weekend edition of First Edition is anchored by CHCH's <A HREF="../biographies/maria.htm">Maria Hayes</A>.

<P>
