<HEAD>

<TITLE>Single Camera/E.F.P. Facilities</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">

<P>
 <HR>

<H1><CENTER>Electronic Field Production</CENTER></H1>
<HR>

<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../gifs/efp.gif"></CENTER> <HR>

<P>
Electonic Field Production (EFP) is fast becoming the mainstay
of television production, in programs, commercials and corporate
videos. It is cost efficient, and with the right package of materials
can provide superior quality production resources on any location
from downtown Hamilton to the Himilayas.
<P>
Our EFP packages are based upon Sony CCD, Beta SP camera platforms
with superior lenses and matte boxes... with a full complement
of filters, lighting and grip gear, as well as the flexible audio
faciltities necessary to provide professional performance in every
application. <BR>
<HR>

<P>
Our EFP unit, which is used extensively for commercial and single
camera corporate work, includes the following equipment:
<UL>
<LI>1 BVP-50 W/Sony Betacam SP Back
<LI>1 BVP-30 W/Sony Beatacam Back (Standard)
<LI>1 Sachtler Tripod with Panhead &amp; Wheels
<LI>1 O'Connor Tripod with Panhead &amp; Wheels
<LI>1 Camera Dolly Platform with 30' of Track
<LI>1 Sachtler Baby Legs
<LI>1 Petroff Matte Box with Filters
<LI>2 Anton Bauer Mini-Lites with Diffusers
<LI>1 Arri Blue Bell Lighting Kits (3 - 1 KW Fixtures Plus with
Stands, 1 Miser Fixture)
<LI>1 Ianabeam Light Kit (3 Fixtures) with Stands
<LI>2 -- 1 KW Soft Lights with Mathews 750 Stands &amp; Wheels
<LI>1 Hard Reflector Board (Hard &amp; Soft sides) with Stand
<LI>3 Flex Fills (2 large, 1 small)
<LI>1 Lowell Umbrella with Stand
<LI>16 NP-Chocolate Bar-style Batteries
<LI>4 -- 12V Camera Battery Belts
<LI>2  Sony Colour Field Monitors (Battery Powered or A.C.)
<LI>4  Lapel Sony ECM-77 Microphones
<LI>Various Hand Microphones
<LI>Sony Monitor Headset
</UL>

<P>
<I>Available upon request:</I>
<UL>
<LI>2  Cetec-Vega Wireless Diversity Microphones
<LI>2  Carbon Fibre Boom Fishpoles
<LI>Several Shotgun Microphones with varying pick-up patterns
(AKG, Sony, Sennheiser) with Blimps
<LI>2  Schure Battery or A.C. Powered 4-input Stereo Mixers
<LI>Additional Lighting, e.g. Hard &amp; Soft source lights from
1KW to 2KW to 5KW fixtures with dimmer pacs
<LI>2 -- BVU-35 Beta SP Record/Playback Units
<LI>1 -- 90 KVA 3 Phase Location Generator
<LI>2 Vans, seating five persons each, with Separate Cargo Area
<LI>1 Utility Truck with 8x12 Box
</UL>
<HR>
<h3>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="postp.htm">Video Post Production</A>
</UL></h3>
<HR>

<P>
<CENTER>Contact: Jim McDougall, Dominic Stanchieri or Wilf Venne,
(905) 522-1101, Toronto Direct Line 366-9688, Fax: 645-3217 or
<BR>
E-mail your questions or comments to
<A HREF="mailto:production@chch.wic.ca">production@chch.wic.ca</A></CENTER>
