<HEAD>

<TITLE>CHCH Production</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">

<P>
 <HR>

<H1><CENTER>Production</CENTER></H1>

<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../gifs/studio2.gif"></CENTER> <HR>

<H2>CORPORATE VIDEO PRODUCTION</H2>

<P>
Corporate Video Production utilizes all of the facilities and
personnel available at CHCH-TV. While most productions are single
camera shoots, we have the capability of multi-camera studio productions
or remotes, as well as teleconferencing.
<P>
Staff writer/producer/directors as well as free-lance personnel
are available to work with clients throughout the video production,
taking charge of the project from conception to completion.
<P>
We will work with clients to establish the objectives of the video,
the information to be transmitted, and the creative approach.
We then script, budget, shoot and edit the video for client approval.
<P>
In most cases, production equipment and personnel are &quot;in-
house&quot;, assuring you of high quality, professional production
standards.<HR>

<H2>COMMERCIAL PRODUCTION</H2>

<P>
Highly skilled and creative writer/producer/directors are on staff
to meet the needs of all types of commercial production. Where
specialized skills or equipment may be needed, CHCH Production
will meet the requirements through the sourcing of free lance
personnel or rental of equipment.
<P>
Our creative personnel work with clients to determine the objectives
of the commercial, and the approximate budget. They then devise
a creative approach, script the commercial, quote the production
costs, and if approval is granted, proceed to produce the commercial.
<BR>
<HR>

<H5>COMMERCIAL &amp; CORPORATE VIDEO CREATIVE PERSONNEL</H5>

<h3><UL>
<LI><A HREF="benedict.htm">Stephen Benedict</A> - <I>Writer/Producer/Director</I>
<LI><A HREF="lambert.htm">Steve Lambert</A> - <I>Writer/Producer/Director</I>
<LI><A HREF="robertsn.htm">Andrew Robertson</A> - <I>Writer/Producer/Director</I>
</UL></h3>
<HR>

<P>
<CENTER>
<P>
For further information, contact: Jim McDougall, (905) 522-1101,
ext. 251,
<P>
Toronto Direct Line 366-9688, Fax: 645-3217 or
<P>
E-mail your questions or comments to
<A HREF="mailto:production@chch.wic.ca">production@chch.wic.ca</A></CENTER>
<HR>

<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></CENTER>
