<HEAD>

<TITLE>Welcome To The New World Wine Tour on the World Wide Web</TITLE>


</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<H1>
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="images/winelogo.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM" ALT="New World Wine Tour Logo">
<IMG SRC="images/barred.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM">
</CENTER>
</H1>

<P>
Demonstrating neither the pretentiousness or pompous rituals that are so often associated with wine tasters, host Jonathan Welsh (E.N.G., Adderly), explores the world of wine and great food on the <B>The New World Wine Tour <I>Niagara</I>.</B>  Each week Jonathan welcomes a different celebrity or personality as his guest for dinner.  Some of the celebrity guests include Red Green, Pierre Berton, Dinah Christie, Camila Scott and Silkan Laumann.   Additionally, Jonathan is joined by Canadian viticulturists and wine makers who provide candid insight on what it is that differentiates one wine from another.

<P>

<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=2>

<TR>
<TH><A HREF="winetour/showprof.htm">About The Show</A></TH>
<TD>An overview of <I>The New World Wine Tour Niagara</I>.</TD>
</TR>
