<TD>Wine making tips, and more, now available on Home Video</TD>
</TR>
<P>
<TR>
<TH><A HREF="winetour/events.htm">The Wine Council of Ontario</A></TH>
<TD>Updated Calendar of Events for 1996!</TD>
</TR>
<P>
<TR><TH><A HREF="winetour/jwelsh.htm">Jonathan Welsh</A></TH>
<TD>Co-Producer/Host</TD>
</TR>
<TR><TH>Wine Resources On The WWW</TH>
<TD>Coming Soon: A look at more wine sites on the Internet.</TD>
</TR>
<P>

</TABLE></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER>
