<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>"Patsy! The Legend Lives On"</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<CENTER><IMG SRC="patsy/patsy.jpg"></CENTER>
<CENTER><H1>&quot;Patsy!&quot;, A Musical Tribute To Patsy Cline,</H1></CENTER>
<CENTER><H2>Now Playing in Toronto</H2></CENTER>
<HR>
Patsy Cline, the country music legend who gave her final concert in 1963 is now more popular than ever!
<P>
The sensational hit musical tribute <I>Patsy!</I> delights audiences and critics alike.  The show features 22 hit songs performed live by award-winning Gail Bliss and backed by a quartet reproducing the sounds of the incredible Jordinaires and a red-hot six-piece country band.  
<P>
The show is a tribute to the spirit of Patsy Cline and a celebration of songs that form one of the greatest legacies in music history.  A legacy honoured with the Grammy Lifetime Achievement award in 1995.
<P>
The legend lives on.

<HR>
<H3>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="patsy/theshow.htm">About The Show</A>
<LI><A HREF="patsy/patsyc.htm">The Real Patsy Cline</A>
<LI><A HREF="patsy/tickets.htm">Ticket and Performance Information</A>
<LI><A HREF="patsy/theatre.htm">The Queen Elizabeth Theatre</A>
<LI><A HREF="patsy/critics.htm">What The Critics Are Saying</A>

</UL>
</H3>


<HR>
<CENTER>| This site is produced and maintained by <A HREF="http://www.chch.com"><I>www.chch.com</I></A> |</CENTER>
<CENTER>| Send your questions or comments to <A HREF="mailto:patsy@chch.wic.ca">patsy@chch.wic.ca</A> |</center>
