<H1><CENTER>Westcom Entertainment Group Ltd.</CENTER></H1>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></CENTER>



<P> Westcom Entertainment coordinates
investments on behalf of WIC's television stations to create quality
programming that will appeal to Canadian and foreign audiences. 
Included on Westcom Entertainment's development slate is a feature film
based on the internationally acclaimed best-selling Canadian novel The
Way of a Boy by Ernest Hillen.  The novel will be adapted for the screen
by Keith Leckie, one of Canada's most accomplished screenwriters, and
produced by Mary Young-Leckie of Perth Avenue Productions 

<P>
