<HEAD>

<TITLE>Integrated Marketing Services</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 2.0z Beta">
</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">

<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/11s.gif"></CENTER>
<CENTER><H1><I>Integrated Marketing Services</I></H1></CENTER>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></CENTER>

<CENTER><H1>Interactive Voice Response</H1></CENTER>
<CENTER><H1>11 In Touch ... Answering the Call</H1></CENTER>
<CENTER><H2>(905) 777-CHCH or toll-free 1-888-770-CHCH</H2></CENTER>

<P>
Consumer desire for product specific information and advertisers
need for measurable results has fueled a tremendous growth in
direct marketing. Responding to these changes is <I><B>11 in Touch</B></I>.
<P>
<I><B>11 in Touch </B></I>is an information service utilizing
state of the art interactive voice response telephone technology
that will harness the power of mass media and delivery precisely
targeted marketing opportunities for today's advertisers.
<P>
Possible IVR Applications:
<PRE>
  * Information Line Sponsorship   * Loyalty Marketing
  * Data Base Building             * Contest Execution
  * Order Fulfillment              * Retail Direct Connect
  * Product Promotion              * Lead Generation
  * Co-promotion
</PRE>
<P>
<B>To explore your company's potential with <I>11 In Touch</I> contact Rob Brignell, (905) 522-1101
extension 166, or send e-mail to <A HREF="mailto:rbrignell@chch.wic.ca">rbrignell@chch.wic.ca</A>.</B>


