<HEAD>

<TITLE>Integrated Marketing Services</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">

<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/11s.gif"></CENTER>
<CENTER><H1><I>Integrated Marketing Services</I></H1></CENTER>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></CENTER>

<CENTER><H2>In Touch On The Internet:<BR>Putting You In Touch with the World</H2></CENTER>
<CENTER><H3>http://www.chch.com/</H3></CENTER>


<P>
The Internet, or &quot;Net&quot;, is a vast computer network that
spans the globe. In the past five years the Internet has experienced
tremendous growth in terms of the technology, consumer awareness,
access and advertising.
<P>
CHCH-TV can assist you in making your transition to this new form
of advertising simple and profitable.
<P>
The Internet is a worthwhile investment. It will be the core of
information network development in the future. Proactive companies
that invest now in understanding its potential will be one step
ahead of their reactive competitors in the future.
<P>
<I><B>Business on the Internet:</B></I>
<P>
* offers business a new method of marketing their goods and services.
<BR>
* provides an inexpensive and effective market tracking.
<BR>
* allows business to provide consumer education about their product
line.
<BR>
* builds business credibility and consumer goodwill.
<BR>
* allows consumers to share product discover information.
<BR>
* business can solicit personnel and volunteers, as well as clientele.
<BR>
* helps support joint partnerships and team efforts within the
organization.
<BR>
* provides a new method for corporate communication, i.e.: brochures,
annual reports, product and service avails, reply cards, etc.

<HR>
<B>To explore your company's potential with <I>In Touch on the Internet</I> contact Rob Brignell, (905) 522-1101, or send e-mail to <A HREF="mailto:intouch@chch.wic.ca">intouch@chch.wic.ca</A>.</B>
<HR>

<CENTER>
<H3><I>CHCH can help your company get on the Information Superhighway
to showcase your company and its products and services to potential
customers around the world!</I></H3>
</CENTER>

<HR>

The CHCH Internet staff can design, create and maintain your own
customized World Wide Web Site, a fully interactive presence on
the Internet!
<P>
Your Web Site is complete with graphics and photos, as much information
as you wish, interactive &quot;forms&quot; for customer feedback,
and direct e-mail capability (or e-mail fax service).
<P>
Your presence on the Internet can:
<UL>
<LI>Highlight your company profile and history
<LI>feature information on your products and services
<LI>profile key staff members
<LI>publicize your address, phone and fax numbers
<LI>Take orders and inquires
</UL>

<P>
The possibilities are ENDLESS!
<P>
CHCH is <I>your</I> Internet specialist. The combination of our
quality, well-designed Web Sites at reasonable rates with our
friendly, helpful staff, add up to <I>your</I> shining presence
on the Internet!

<HR>

<CENTER><H1>Our Web Site Packages</H1></CENTER>

<CENTER>
<I>Our Web Site packages offer something for everyone. From the
smallest of home-based businesses, to larger corporate pages,
CHCH can design a site suitable to your needs.</I>
</CENTER>


<H2>The Basic (Small) Site:</H2>

<P>
Aimed at the small business or individual, this package provides
all the necessities at a minimum cost.
<UL>
<LI>Construction using up to 5 pages of information (300 words
per page)
<LI>2 graphic/photo captures
<LI>direct e-mail link to your e-mail address or e-mail fax service
<LI>up to 6 months Web Site hosting
</UL>

<P>

<H2>The Business Site:</H2>

<P>
Ideal for the medium-sized business or company, this site is of
great value at a great price.
<UL>
<LI>Construction using up to 8 pages of information (300 words
per page)
<LI>5 graphic/photo captures
<LI>1 &quot;clickable&quot; imagemap. Image supplied by you.
<LI>direct e-mail link to your e-mail address or e-mail fax service
<LI>up to 6 months Web Site hosting
</UL>


<H2>The Corporate Site:</H2>

<P>
<EM><B>A great value for the larger company, this site allows
you to present a large amount of information on the Web.</B></EM>
<UL>
<LI>Construction using up to 12 pages of information (300 words
per page)
<LI>7 graphic/photo captures
<LI>2 &quot;clickable&quot; imagemaps. Images supplied by you.
<LI>direct e-mail link to your e-mail address or e-mail fax service
<LI>up to 6 months Web Site hosting
</UL>

<P>
Each Web Site Package Includes:
<UL>
<LI>registration of your site on the top 10 WWW search engines
<LI>a link to your site from the CHCH Corporate Associates Page
<LI>necessary hypertext links within your site
<LI>&quot;interactive&quot; on-line forms as needed
</UL>
<HR>
<B>To explore your company's potential with <I>In Touch on the Internet</I> contact Rob Brignell, (905) 522-1101, or send e-mail to <A HREF="mailto:intouch@chch.wic.ca">intouch@chch.wic.ca</A>.</B>

<P>
