<HEAD>

<TITLE>"Suddenly Susan", New This Fall on CHCH-TV</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../../images/bkgd.jpg">
<P>

<CENTER><IMG HEIGHT=96 WIDTH=504 SRC="../../images/fall96.gif"></CENTER>

<CENTER>
<H1><I><B>Suddenly Susan</B></I></H1>
</CENTER>


<P>
<B>Brooke Shields</B> stars as Susan, a bright, beautiful book
editor who has led a sheltered life.  Now, as she faces a new
career position, she also, for the first time, faces life as a
woman on her own -- having just ended a relationship with her
live-in boyfriend.  Both situations are frightening and exhilarating,
but Susan is learning all she needs to know about single life
from her co-worker and best friend Marcy.  Meanwhile, at work,
Susan is put through her paces by Charlotte, a flamboyant and
wildly eccentric romance novelist.  
<P>
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="../../images/bar.gif" WIDTH=585 HEIGHT=30 BORDER=0>
