<HEAD>

<TITLE>"Dark Skies", New This Fall on CHCH-TV</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../../images/bkgd.jpg">
<P>

<CENTER><IMG HEIGHT=96 WIDTH=504 SRC="../../images/fall96.gif"></CENTER>

<CENTER>
<H1><I><B>Dark Skies</B></I></H1>
</CENTER>


<P>
This epic science fiction-adventure series, combining 40 years
of history occurring in the late 20th century and speculative
fiction, leads to a final showdown between humans and aliens on
the eve of the millennium.  Leading the battle to save the world
are John Loengard and his girlfriend Kimberly Sayers, who, as
two utopian college grads in 1961, went to Washington to join
John F. Kennedy's New Frontier.  When Loengard stumbles into an
ultrasecret government program to fight a covert invasion of the
planet by extraterrestrial intelligence, he and Kimberly become
both victims and warriors in a resistance movement known as &quot;Dark
Skies.&quot;   The secret war will involve not only them, but
their children and millions more as well.  

<P>
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="../../images/bar.gif" WIDTH=585 HEIGHT=30 BORDER=0>
<H3><B><I>Dark Skies</I></B> on the WEB:</H3>
