<P>
<B>Eric Close</B> (<I>Sisters</I>),<B> Megan Ward</B> and <B>J.T.
Walsh</B> star.  Executive Producer/Writer: Bryce Zabel (<I>Lois
&amp; Clark, Life Goes On, L.A. Law</I>); Executive Producer:
Joseph Stern  (<I>Law &amp; Order</I>); Supervising Producer/Writer:
Brent V. Friedman (<I>The Resurrected, The Dentist</I>); Director:
Tobe Hooper (<I>Poltergeist, Nowhere Man</I>).  Production Company:
Columbia Pictures Television in association with Rosecrans Productions.
       
