<TITLE>"The Pretender", New This Fall on CHCH-TV</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../../images/bkgd.jpg">
<P>

<CENTER><IMG HEIGHT=96 WIDTH=504 SRC="../../images/fall96.gif"></CENTER>

<CENTER>
<H1><I><B>The Pretender</B></I></H1>
</CENTER>


<P>

Jarod, a genius raised in isolation by a secret organization and
trained to be a &quot;human chameleon,&quot; flees &quot;The Centre&quot;
after discovering his brilliant studies were used to stage misdeeds.
 Utilizing his charm and ability to assume any personality and
solve any puzzle, Jarod takes on new identities and tasks, weekly,
to make up for the wrongs he inadvertently caused, all the while
being pursued by people who want him stopped -- dead.  <B> </B>
<P>

<HR>
<I>Credits for<B> The Pretender</B>:</I>
<P>
<B>Michael T. Weiss, Andrea Parker </B>and <B>Patrick Bachau</B>
star.  Executive Producer/Writers: Steven Long Mitchell (<I>Alien
Nation</I>), Craig W. Van Sickle (<I>Alien Nation</I>); Executive
Producer/Director Rick Wallace (<I>L.A. Law</I>).  Production
Company: MTM Enterprises, Inc.     
       
