<HEAD>

<TITLE>"Profiler", New This Fall on CHCH-TV</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../../images/bkgd.jpg">
<P>

<CENTER><IMG HEIGHT=96 WIDTH=504 SRC="../../images/fall96.gif"></CENTER>

<CENTER>
<H1><I><B>Profiler</B></I></H1>
</CENTER>


<P>
In the style of <I>Silence of the Lambs</I>, <I><B>Profiler</B></I>
is about a brilliant, reclusive, former FBI forensic psychologist,
Samantha Waters, who is brought back by the Bureau to solve an
unusual series of killings in Atlanta.  &quot;Sam,&quot; the best
in observing the salient subtleties of a crime, originally left
the Bureau after a deadly game of cat-and-mouse with a clever
serial killer, nicknamed Jack (for Jack-of-all-trades), resulted
in her husband's murder.  Now, Jack is back and Sam, knowing he
wants to find her, has returned on her own terms.  
<P>
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="../../images/bar.gif" WIDTH=585 HEIGHT=30 BORDER=0>
