<B>and Roma Maffia</B> star.  Executive Producers: Ian Sander
(<I>I'll Fly Away</I>) and Kim Moses (<I>New York News</I>); Supervising
Producer/Writer: Cynthia Saunders (<I>L.A. Law, Equal Justice</I>);
Director: John Patterson (<I>Law &amp; Order</I> pilot).  Production
