<HEAD>

<TITLE>"Relativity", New This Fall on CHCH-TV</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../../images/bkgd.jpg">
<P>

<CENTER><IMG HEIGHT=96 WIDTH=504 SRC="../../images/fall96.gif"></CENTER>

<CENTER>
<H1><I><B>Relativity</B></I></H1>
</CENTER>

<P>
From the creators of<I> thirtysomething </I>and<I> My So-Called
Life,</I> comes a romantic comedy focused on the mirth and madness
of marriage and extended families.  Isabel and Leo, the central
characters, meet and fall in love while Isabel is still engaged
to another man named Everett.  As many know only too well, the
road to true love is not smooth and the sources of Leo's anxieties
include Isabel's unreliable father, an opinionated gay sister
and  a fear that Isabel will one day return to Everett.  Love,
however, will prevail.
<P>

