<HEAD>

<TITLE>"Turning Point", This Fall on CHCH-TV</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../../images/bkgd.jpg">
<P>

<CENTER><IMG HEIGHT=96 WIDTH=504 SRC="../../images/fall96.gif"></CENTER>

<CENTER>
<H1><I><B>Turning Point</B></I></H1>
</CENTER>

<P>
Combining in-depth news coverage with powerful storytelling, <I><B>Turning
Point</B></I> focuses on the most compelling stories from today's
headlines and, for one unique hour, details the drama of that
event and how it changed people's lives forever.  Whether it's
a world-renowned news event, a personal drama, or a decision which
altered the course of history, rotating anchors <B>Forrest Sawyer,
Diane Sawyer</B> and <B>Barbara Walters</B> get to the heart of
the story.  
<P>

<HR>
<I>Credits for<B> Turning Point</B>:</I> 
<P>
Journalists <B>Forrest Sawyer, Diane Sawyer</B> and <B>Barbara
Walters</B> anchor this newsmagazine on a rotating basis.  <I><B>Turning
Point</B></I> is an ABC News Production.

